{%- comment -%}
cloak_status — small status line. Demonstrates {% include %} from the
base layout's default status block. Single point of localisation for the
cloak-state readout.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if world.wearing_cloak -%}Cloak: worn{%- else -%}Cloak: hung up{%- endif -%}{%- if world.disturbance > 0 -%}  |  Disturbance: {{ world.disturbance }}{%- endif -%}
